#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Sissejuhatus"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Launching &kfind;"
msgstr "&kfind;i käivitamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Find Files tool is a useful method of searching for specific files on "
"your computer, or for searching for files that match a pattern. An example "
"of this could include searching for files of a particular type or with "
"certain letters in the filename. You can load this utility in &konqueror; "
"(in file manager mode) by selecting <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></keycombo></shortcut><guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Find File</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the menu. If "
"you want to use &kfind; as a standalone search tool, launch it by using "
"&krunner;."
msgstr ""
"Failide otsimise abivahend on äärmiselt kasulik kindla faili või teatud "
"mustrile vastavate failide leidmiseks arvutis. Nii on võimalik näiteks "
"otsida teatud tüüpi või nimes teatud tähti sisaldavaid faile. Abivahendi "
"saab avada &konqueror;is (failihalduri režiimis), kui valida menüükäsk "
"<menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; <keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo></shortcut><guimenu>Tööriistad</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Failide "
"otsimine</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Kui soovid aga kasutada &kfind;i "
"omaette otsingutööriistana, käivita see &krunner;i vahendusel."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Finding Files"
msgstr "Failide otsimine"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Name/Location Tab"
msgstr "Nime/asukoha kaart"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When starting &kfind;, you will see a quite simple window. Type in the name "
"of the file you are searching for in the text box labeled <guilabel>Named:</"
"guilabel>. You can use wildcard matching and a semicolon (<quote>;</quote>) "
"for separating multiple names."
msgstr ""
"&kfind;i käivitamisel ilmub üsna lihtne aken. Kirjuta otsitava faili nimi "
"tekstikasti <guilabel>Nimi:</guilabel>. Soovi korral võib kasutada metamärke "
"ning mitme nime eraldamiseks semikoolonit (<quote>;</quote>)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose a folder where you want to search by typing it in the field "
"<guilabel>Look in:</guilabel> or by clicking <guibutton>Browse...</"
"guibutton> (you can toggle the display of the hidden files and folder in the "
"dialog using the shortcuts <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>.</"
"keycap></keycombo> or <keycap>F8</keycap>) and press &Enter; or click the "
"<guibutton>Find</guibutton> button. Use the <guibutton>Stop</guibutton> "
"button to cancel a search. A search result can be saved in &HTML; format or "
"as plain text with the <guibutton>Save As...</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Kataloogi, milles otsida, saab kirjutada väljale <guilabel>Asukoht:</"
"guilabel> või valida klõpsates nupule <guibutton>Lehitse...</guibutton> "
"(peidetud failide ja kataloogide kuvamist dialoogis saab muuta "
"kiirklahvidega  <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>.</keycap></"
"keycombo> või <keycap>F8</keycap>). Seejärel vajuta &Enter; või klõpsa "
"nupule <guibutton>Otsi</guibutton>. Nupuga <guibutton>Peata</guibutton> saab "
"otsimise katkestada. Otsingutulemused võib salvestada &HTML;-vormingusse või "
"lihttekstina nupu <guibutton>Salvesta kui...</guibutton> abil."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Include subfolders</guilabel> is checked all subfolders "
"starting from your chosen folder will be searched too. If you enable "
"<guilabel>Case sensitive search</guilabel>, &kfind; will only find files "
"with the exact case matching names. Enable the option <guilabel>Show hidden "
"files</guilabel> to include them in your search. Selecting <guilabel>Use "
"files index</guilabel> lets you use the files' index created by the "
"<quote>locate</quote> package to speed-up the search."
msgstr ""
"Kui märgitud on <guilabel>Kaasa arvatud alamkataloogid</guilabel>, otsitakse "
"läbi ka kõik valitud kataloogi alamkataloogid. Kui märkida "
"<guilabel>Tõstutundlik otsing</guilabel>, leiab &kfind; ainult failid, mille "
"puhul sobivad otsitavaga täpselt ka tähesuurused. Valiku <guilabel>Peidetud "
"failide näitamine</guilabel> märkimisel kaasatakse otsingusse ka sellised "
"failid. Valik <guilabel>Failiindeksi kasutamine</guilabel> võimaldab "
"tarvitada failide indeksit, mille loob otsingu kiirendamiseks programm "
"<quote>locate</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can use the following wildcards for file or folder names:"
msgstr "Faili- või katalooginimede puhul saab kasutada järgmisi metamärke:"

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Asterisk <quote><keycap>*</keycap></quote>"
msgstr "Tärn <quote><keycap>*</keycap></quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The asterisk stands for any number of missing characters (even zero), that "
"means &eg; searching for <userinput>marc*</userinput> may find the files "
"<filename>marc</filename>, <filename>marc.png</filename> and <filename> "
"marc_must_not_read_this.kwd</filename>. <userinput>mar*.kwd</userinput> may "
"find <filename>marketplace.kwd</filename> and "
"<filename>marc_must_not_read_this.kwd</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Tärn tähistab suvalist hulka puuduvaid märke (ka mitte ühtegi), see "
"tähendab, et &eg; otsingufraas <userinput>marek*</userinput> annab "
"tulemuseks <filename>marek</filename>, <filename>marek.png</filename> ja "
"<filename>marek_ei_tohi_seda_lugeda.kwd</filename>. Samas <userinput>mare*."
"kwd</userinput> leiab näiteks <filename>maretädi.kwd</filename> ja "
"<filename>marek_ei_tohi_seda_lugeda.kwd</filename>."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Question Mark <quote><keycap>?</keycap></quote>"
msgstr "Küsimärk <quote><keycap>?</keycap></quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In contrast to the asterisk, the question mark stands for exactly one "
"character, so <userinput>mar?</userinput> will find <filename>marc</"
"filename>, but <userinput>marc?</userinput> will not find anything, as our "
"files are called <filename>marc</filename> and <filename>marc.png</"
"filename>. You can put as many question marks in the term as you want, it "
"will find exactly that number of characters."
msgstr ""
"Erinevalt tärnist tähistab küsimärk täpselt üht puuduvat märki, nii et "
"<userinput>mare?</userinput> tulemuseks on <filename>marek</filename>, kuid "
"<userinput>marek?</userinput> ei leia midagi, sest failide nimed on "
"<filename>marek</filename> ja <filename>marek.png</filename>. Küsimärke võib "
"otsingusse kirjutada nii palju, kui süda lustib, pidades aga silmas, et "
"igaühele vastab üks märk."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Character Set <quote>[...]</quote>"
msgstr "Kooditabel <quote>[...]</quote>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid "This matches any of the characters between the braces."
msgstr "Vastab iga sulgudes olev märk."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Of course you can combine two or more wildcard symbols in a search term."
msgstr ""
"Mõistagi on kaht või rohkematki metamärki võimalik otsingus ka kombineerida."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The results of your search will be displayed in the box below. A click with "
"the &RMB; on a selection in this box opens a context menu with a list of "
"actions for the selected files or folders."
msgstr ""
"Otsingutulemusi näeb allolevas kastis. Klõps &HPNga; selles kastis olevale "
"kirjele avab kontekstimenüü, mis sisaldab rohkelt toiminguid, mida on "
"valitud faili või kataloogiga võimalik ette võtta."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Contents Tab"
msgstr "Sisu kaart"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "File type"
msgstr "Failitüüp"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you can specify the type of file you are searching for."
msgstr "Siin saab määrata, millist tüüpi faile tuleb otsida."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:171
#, no-c-format
msgid "Containing text"
msgstr "Sisaldab teksti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Type in the word or phrase the files you are searching for must contain. "
"Note: If you do this in a large folder or checked <guilabel>Include "
"subfolders</guilabel> in the <guilabel>Name/Location</guilabel> tab, this "
"may take a long time."
msgstr ""
"Kirjuta siia sõna või fraas, mida otsitav fail peab sisaldama. Märkus: Kui "
"rakendad seda võimalust suure kataloogi puhul või kui kaardil <guilabel>Nimi/"
"Asukoht</guilabel> on ära märgitud kast <guilabel>Kaasa arvatud "
"alamkataloogid</guilabel>, võib see võtta päris palju aega."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This option will <emphasis>not</emphasis> work for all files listed under "
"<guilabel>File type</guilabel>. Only the following file types are supported:"
msgstr ""
"See võimalus <emphasis>ei</emphasis> toimi kõigi failide puhul, mille toob "
"ära <guilabel>failitüüp</guilabel>. Toetatud on ainult järgmised failitüübid:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text files, &eg; source code and <filename>README</filename> files"
msgstr "Tekstifailid, &eg; lähtekoodi ja <filename>README</filename> failid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "OpenOffice.org Writer / LibreOffice Writer"
msgstr "OpenOffice.org Writer / LibreOffice Writer"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:187
#, no-c-format
msgid "OpenOffice.org Impress / LibreOffice Impress"
msgstr "OpenOffice.org Impress / LibreOffice Impress"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "OpenOffice.org Calc / LibreOffice Calc"
msgstr "OpenOffice.org Calc / LibreOffice Calc"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calligra Words"
msgstr "Calligra Words"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calligra Sheets"
msgstr "Calligra Sheets"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "Calligra Stage"
msgstr "Calligra Stage"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid "Case sensitive"
msgstr "Tõstutundlik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you enable this option, &kfind; will only find text in files with the "
"exact case matching, &eg; <userinput>MARC</userinput> will only match "
"<quote>MARC</quote>, not <quote>Marc</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Selle sisselülitamisel leiab &kfind; ainult teksti failides, mis vastavad "
"täpselt otsitavale, &eg; otsingule <userinput>MAREK</userinput> vastab "
"ainult <quote>MAREK</quote>, aga mitte <quote>Marek</quote>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "Regular expression"
msgstr "Regulaarvaldis"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have installed the &kregexpeditor; tool from playground/utils on the "
"&kde; git server, you will have this additional option. Enabling it will "
"allow you to search for a <firstterm>regexp</firstterm> or regular "
"expression. A regexp is a way to specify conditions for your search, and "
"they can be very complex, and equally they can be very powerful. If you are "
"unfamiliar with regular expressions, you can choose <guibutton>Edit</"
"guibutton> button to open &kregexpeditor;. This tool allows you to construct "
"your set of conditions graphically, and then generates the expression for "
"you."
msgstr ""
"Kui paigaldatud on &kde; Git-serveris playground/utils all leiduv "
"&kregexpeditor;, on võimalik kasutada sellist lisavõimalust. Selle lubamine "
"võimaldab kasutada otsimisel <firstterm>regexp</firstterm>-i ehk "
"regulaaravaldist. Regulaaravaldis on meetod piiritleda otsingutingimusi, "
"selle võimalused võivad olla päris keerukad, kuid samas väga võimsad. Kui "
"regulaaravaldised sulle väga tuttavad ei ole, võid vajutada nuppu "
"<guibutton>Muuda...</guibutton>, mis avab &kregexpeditor;i. See lubab sul "
"oma tingimused graafiliselt määrata ning koostab siis sinu eest korrektse "
"avaldise."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kregexpeditor; is a very useful tool, and can be used from within many "
"&kde; applications other than &kfind;. You can find more information from "
"within its own help file."
msgstr ""
"&kregexpeditor; on väga kasulik vahend, mida saab kasutada ka palju enamate "
"&kde; rakenduste puhul kui pelgalt &kfind;. Rohkem infot selle kohta leiab "
"tema käsiraamatust."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include binary files"
msgstr "Kaasa arvatud binaarfailid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This lets you search in any type of file, even those that usually do not "
"contain text (for example program files and images)."
msgstr ""
"See võimaldab otsida suvalist tüüpi faile, ka neid, mis tavaliselt ei "
"sisalda teksti (näiteks programmifailid ja pildid)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search metainfo sections"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These two fields can be used to search within files' specific comments or "
"metainfo."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here are some major cases:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Video files (avi, mp4, &etc;)</emphasis>: specify some tag "
"(<userinput>Bitrate</userinput>, <userinput>Duration</userinput>, &etc;) and "
"its value to find items which have the specified parameter value in their "
"metadata."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:253
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Images (png, jpeg, &etc;)</emphasis>: specify some tag "
"(<userinput>Width</userinput>, <userinput>Height</userinput>, &etc;) and its "
"value to find items which have the specified parameter value in their "
"metadata."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Audio files (mp3, flac, &etc;)</emphasis>: specify some tag "
"(<userinput>Title</userinput>, <userinput>Album</userinput>, &etc;) and its "
"value to find items which have the specified parameter value in their "
"metadata."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis>Ebooks (epub, azw, fb2, &etc;)</emphasis>: specify some tag "
"(<userinput>Title</userinput>, <userinput>Author</userinput>, &etc;) and its "
"value to find items which have the specified parameter value in their "
"metadata."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:269
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there is a translation of the tags into your language you can use the "
"localized tag names in the search criterion."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:280
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Properties Tab"
msgstr "Omaduste kaart"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can refine your search. These are the special refinements you can "
"choose:"
msgstr ""
"Siin saab täpsustada otsingu tingimusi. Valida saab järgmiste piirajate "
"vahel:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:290
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find all files created or modified"
msgstr "Otsitakse faile, mis on loodud või mida on muudetud:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can either enter two dates, between which the files were created or "
"modified, or specify a time period."
msgstr ""
"Siin saab sisestada kaks kuupäeva, mille vahel peavad failid olema loodud "
"või muudetud, või määrata periood."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid "File size is"
msgstr "Faili suurus on:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:302
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can specify if the file has to be at least or at most as big as the "
"size you entered in the following box, or else equal to the size."
msgstr "Siin saab määrata otsitava faili vähima või suurima suuruse."

#. Tag: term
#: index.docbook:310
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Files owned by user</guilabel>, <guilabel>Files owned by group</"
"guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Faili omanikuks on kasutaja</guilabel> ja <guilabel>Faili grupp "
"on</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:312
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you can specify user and group names as owner of the files."
msgstr "Siin saab määrata faili(de) kasutaja ja grupi nime."

